<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>로그인</title>
    <style>
        /* 전체 기본 스타일 초기화 */
        body {
            font-family: 'Pretendard', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        /* 로그인 카드 박스 */
        .login-container {
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 100%;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        /* 상단 타이틀 */
        .login-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .login-header h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #111;
            margin: 0 0 8px 0;
        }

        .login-header p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #868e96;
            margin: 0;
        }

        /* 폼 입력 요소 */
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .form-group label {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #495057;
        }

        /* 인풋 상자 스타일 */
        input[type="text"],
        input[type="password"] {
            width: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            padding: 12px 14px;
            border: 1px solid #ced4da;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 15px;
            transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
            background-color: #fff;
        }

        /* 마우스 클릭 시 빛나는 효과 */
        input[type="text"]:focus,
        input[type="password"]:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #80bdff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.2rem rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.25);
        }

        /* 로그인 버튼 */
        .btn-login {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 10px;
            transition: background-color 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-login:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }

        /* 하단 보조 메뉴 링크 */
        .login-footer {
            margin-top: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #666;
            border-top: 1px solid #f1f3f5;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }

        .login-footer a {
            color: #0066cc;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .login-footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="login-container">

    <div class="login-header">
        <h2>🔑 로그인</h2>
        <p>서비스 이용을 위해 로그인이 필요합니다.</p>
    </div>

    <form action="/user/login" method="POST">

        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="username">아이디</label>
            <input type="text" id="username" name="username" placeholder="아이디를 입력하세요" required>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="password">비밀번호</label>
            <input type="password" id="password" name="password" placeholder="비밀번호를 입력하세요" required>
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="btn-login">로그인</button>

    </form>

    <div class="login-footer">
        아직 계정이 없으신가요? <a href="/user/register">회원가입 하기</a>
    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>